Name
       timing_report_enable_unique_pins_multiple_capture_clock_paths

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_unique_pins_multiple_capture_clock_paths

       Default: false

       Enables  reporting  of  different  paths  with respect to the reference
       clocks in the unique pins.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

